herdr
======

herdr is a fork of claudectl (https://github.com/mercurialsolo/claudectl),
licensed under the MIT License, Copyright (c) 2026 mercurialsolo.

The crates under `crates/claudectl-core` and `crates/claudectl-tui` are
vendored from claudectl at commit:

    9c15a506452fc6df499c9241d2373256c2135197  (v0.57.2-8-g9c15a506)

Only the lean, synchronous data + render layer was vendored. The upstream
brain / bus / coord orchestrator (the root binary crate's `src/brain`,
`src/bus`, `src/coord` modules, which depend on tokio + rmcp + rusqlite) was
deliberately excluded. See CLAUDE.md §1 and the Phase 0 plan for rationale.

The original MIT license text is retained in LICENSE.
